war.model

Class EngineeringModelData

  • java.lang.Object
    • war.model.EngineeringModelData

  • @Entity
public class EngineeringModelData
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing data from the concrete deterioration engineering model output. It associates values with the climate variables and climate parameters.
    Since:
    20th Dec. 2012
    Author:
    Guillaume Prevost
